@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ijrxqq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.09 / v1 + 0.86)) / (v0 + v2))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v2 + 0.29) * (v0 + 0.11 / v0 + 0.02)))
    v0 = ((0.58 + 0.71) / wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.16)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.72)) * tmp)
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
